cation=Chennai, India|accessdate=12 July 2013|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130701114803/https://www.thehindu.com/features/friday-review/travails-of-a-genius/article4857108.ece|archivedate=1 July 2013}}</ref>
